  "notes": [
    "sunburst_v2 是标准 chart data API 图，不是 legacy chart；查询由 Sunburst/buildQuery.ts 基于 buildQueryContext() 构造。",
    "字段名优先取 controlPanel 配置中的 name；如 transformProps/types 中确认了 camelCase 运行时别名，则补充 runtime_alias。",
    "Sunburst 图的核心输入是 columns、metric 和可选的 secondary_metric。transformProps 会把 columns 转成 columnLabels，再交给 utils/treeBuilder.ts 构建多层树。",
    "columns 在源码层没有 validateNonEmpty 校验，但 treeBuilder 直接依赖 groupBy/columns 作为层级输入；从图表语义上它是高重要字段。",
    "secondary_metric 存在时，transformProps 会切换到 linearColorScheme，并按 secondary_metric / metric 比值计算线性颜色；否则使用 color_scheme 的分类色。",
    "sort_by_metric 并不是纯显示字段；Sunburst/buildQuery.ts 会在其为真时写入 orderby=[[metric,false]]。",
    "Sunburst controlPanel 没有 Chart Title、Advanced analytics、Annotations、Forecast 等 section。",
    "embedding 仅在字段命中 superset-ui-core/query/constants.ts 的 extra_form_data append/override 白名单时标记为可用。"
  ],
  "control_overrides": {
    "metric": {
      "label": "Primary Metric",
      "description": "The primary metric is used to define the arc segment sizes"
    },
    "secondary_metric": {
      "label": "Secondary Metric",
      "default_value": null,
      "description": "[optional] this secondary metric is used to define the color as a ratio against the primary metric. When omitted, the color is categorical and based on labels"
    },
    "color_scheme": {
      "description": "When only a primary metric is provided, a categorical color scale is used."
    },
    "linear_color_scheme": {
      "description": "When a secondary metric is provided, a linear color scale is used."
    },
    "columns": {
      "label": "Hierarchy",
      "description": "Sets the hierarchy levels of the chart. Each level is represented by one ring with the innermost circle as the top of the hierarchy."
    }
  },
  "form_data_overrides": {
